languages.text: "Не ведомый очевидной наживой, твой разум предсказуемо слаб и ленив. Пытливому разведчику очевидно, что мы приблизились к кладезю данных".
"As expected, your sluggish and feeble mind is ignorant of the obvious bounty at hand. Any inquisitive explorer would realise that we are near a great source of Knowledge."

languages.text: “不出意料，你那迟钝、软弱的头脑对眼前这一目了然的宝藏一无所知。每位充满好奇的探险家都能意识到，我们正在接近某个伟大的知识来源。”

languages.text: «Como esperaba, su mente lenta y débil ignora el regalo que tenemos ante nuestros ojos. Cualquier explorador inquisitivo comprendería que nos encontramos junto a una gran fuente de conocimiento».
languages.original_text: "As expected, your sluggish and feeble mind is ignorant of the obvious bounty at hand. Any inquisitive explorer would realise that we are near a great source of Knowledge."

languages.text: 「予想通り、あなたの鈍重で弱々しい心は、目の前にある明らかな賞金に気づいていないようですね。好奇心旺盛な探検家なら、ここが知識の宝庫の近くだと気づくはずです」
languages.original_text: "As expected, your sluggish and feeble mind is ignorant of the obvious bounty at hand. Any inquisitive explorer would realise that we are near a great source of Knowledge."

traits.speaker: PasqalQuest_Dements

languages.text: "Wie erwartet, ist Euer schwerfälliger und dürftiger Verstand blind für die offensichtliche Beute, die uns erwartet. Jeder wissbegierige Forscher würde erkennen, dass wir uns in der Nähe eines grandiosen Quells des Wissens befinden."
languages.original_text: "As expected, your sluggish and feeble mind is ignorant of the obvious bounty at hand. Any inquisitive explorer would realise that we are near a great source of Knowledge."

languages.text: « Comme il fallait s'y attendre, votre esprit ignorant est aveugle à la munificence de ce qui l'entoure... Un véritable explorateur se rendrait tout de suite compte que nous sommes près d'une grande source de connaissance. »
